### Test Loyalty Platform Integration
### Make sure both apps are running:
### - Loyalty Platform: http://localhost:3000
### - GOK Cafe API: http://localhost:5000 (or your port)

### 1. Test Loyalty Platform - Get All Vouchers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouchers
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Test Loyalty Platform - Get User Vouchers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vouchers/user/test-user-guid
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. GOK Cafe - Fetch Vouchers from Loyalty Platform (Preview)
### Replace {admin-token} with your actual admin JWT token
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/loyaltyplatform/vouchers/fetch
Authorization: Bearer {admin-token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. GOK Cafe - Sync Vouchers from Loyalty Platform
### Replace {admin-token} with your actual admin JWT token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/loyaltyplatform/vouchers/sync
Authorization: Bearer {admin-token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. GOK Cafe - Verify Synced Coupons
### Replace {admin-token} with your actual admin JWT token
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/coupons?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {admin-token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. GOK Cafe - Get Specific Coupon by Code
### Replace the code with an actual voucher code from loyalty platform
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/coupons/code/WELCOME10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 7. GOK Cafe - Validate Coupon (Before Applying)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/coupons/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "WELCOME10",
  "orderAmount": 200,
  "userId": "your-user-guid-here"
}

###

### 8. GOK Cafe - Apply Coupon to Order
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/coupons/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "WELCOME10",
  "orderAmount": 200,
  "userId": "your-user-guid-here",
  "sessionId": "session-123"
}

###
